Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:01.64,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:01.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:06.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま…また昨日も心臓麻痺の犠牲者が23人?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:06.64,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,There were another 23 victims yesterday, again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:09.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キラは学生かもしれないという疑いが生じたとたん、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:12.74,Default,L,0,0,0,,As soon as the possibility of Kira being a student is put forward, the timing of the murders change to indicate that this isn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:12.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを否定するような殺人が起こった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:15.70,Default,L,0,0,0,,I guess this means that Kira must have access to police information.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:15.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キラは警察の情報を知っているという事か…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:18.57,Default-ja,,0,0,5,,僕に捜査状況が洩れたと知った{\fs14} {\fnCloister Black\fe120\fs30}L{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs14} {\fs24}は…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:22.87,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Now that L knows I'm somehow getting police information, without doubt, he'll use the police as a link to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:22.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,警察内部から、僕への糸口をつかもうとするに決まっている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:26.81,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,There's a human that's been following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっとお前をつけている人間がいる…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:30.96,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Looks like I've got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:30.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは邪魔だな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:33.13,Default,Light,0,0,0,,I'll have to get rid of him as soon as possible, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:33.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるべく早く消してやるよ、リュック
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:39.80,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,A Shinigami's eyes have the ability to see a person's name and life span, just by looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:35.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死神の目には…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:40.72,Note,NOTE,0,0,0,,Yagami Light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:39.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつの名前と寿命が顔の上に見えるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:40.91,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Also, {\alpha&HFF&}Shinigami have the ability to change the eyes of any human who finds their notebook, into the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:44.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして、死神は自分の落としたノートを拾った人間の目を…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Shinigami have the ability to change the eyes of any human who finds their notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}into the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Shinigami have the ability to change the eyes of any human who finds their notebook, into the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:47.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死神の目にしてやる事ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:51.30,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,The price for a Shinigami's eyes is... {\alpha&HFF&}half of your remaining life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:50.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}目　玉　　　　　\N{\fs24}死神の眼球の値段は…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The price for a Shinigami's eyes is... half of your remaining life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:55.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その人間の残りの寿命の…半分だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:01:00.03,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,So, what do you want to do, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:59.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さぁ…どうする？ライト
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:03.04,SIGN,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs72\pos(362,361)}The Chase
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.29,Default,Shinigami,0,0,0,,Haven't seen Ryuk around lately, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:06.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最近、リュークみねぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:09.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}デスノート　{\fs24}　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　\N下界に日記帳を落としたのってマジだったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:09.76,Default,Shinigami,0,0,0,,Was he serious about having dropped his Death Note on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:12.68,Default,Shinigami,0,0,0,,It must have been picked up by a human before he got to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:12.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で、先人間に拾われたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:19.41,Default,Shinigami,0,0,0,,No way! If he did something like that, he'd be forced to watch over them until either the human dies, or the notebook is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:13.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んなことしたら拾った奴の最後がノートの最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:18.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見届けなきゃいけねぇんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:23.49,Default,Shinigami,0,0,0,,You're right. There's no way Ryuk could be bothered to do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:23.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だな、そんな面倒くせぇ事リュークがするはずがねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:27.65,Default,Shinigami,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I heard he's got two Death Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:27.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}　　デスノート{\fs24}\Nしかもアイツ…二冊日記帳持てたって話だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:30.59,Default,Shinigami,0,0,0,,Seriously?! Why the hell has he got two?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:30.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジか？何のために二冊が？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:32.90,Default,Shinigami,0,0,0,,I just don't understand the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:32.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつのやる事はわからん…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:36.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕が死神の目を持つためには…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:37.49,Default,Light,0,0,0,,So, in order for me to acquire the eyes of a Shinigami, {\alpha&HFF&}I've got to give up half of my remaining life span... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in order for me to acquire the eyes of a Shinigami, I've got to give up half of my remaining life span... {\alpha&HFF&}right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:39.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寿命の半分を差し出さなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in order for me to acquire the eyes of a Shinigami, I've got to give up half of my remaining life span... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:41.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…そうだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:45.02,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Yeah, so what do ya wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ、どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.33,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Have we got a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.14,0:01:46.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取引するか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:50.69,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Ryuk.. {\alpha&HFF&}that deal is... out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:48.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リューク、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuk.. that deal is... {\alpha&HFF&}out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:53.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この取引…論外だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuk.. that deal is... out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:54.46,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:54.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいかリューク
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:08.02,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to create a new ideal world, free of criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:11.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は犯罪者のいない理想の新世界をつくる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:15.44,Default,Light,0,0,0,,And I intend to reign as God of that new world for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:15.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして、そこの世界の神として、長く君臨するんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:19.03,Default,Light,0,0,0,,If the deal had involved increasing my life span, I might have considered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:20.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の寿命が延びるんなら考えるが、短くなるんじゃ話にならない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:20.86,Default,Light,0,0,0,,But anything that decreases it isn't even worth discussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:24.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことリュークだって判ってる筈だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:24.39,Default,Light,0,0,0,,I'd have thought that you'd already know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:29.28,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Yeah. Well, I just wanted to tell you that the deal exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:24.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ、そういう取引もあると言いたかっただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:33.54,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Thought I'd better tell you this sort of thing early on, so I don't have to put up with your complaints later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:33.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こういう話は早くしておかないと後で文句言われても嫌だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:36.88,Default,Light,0,0,0,,You thought you'd better tell me this sort of thing "early on"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:36.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こういう話は早くしておかないと？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.18,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Isn't it already slightly late?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:38.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら言うの遅いだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:41.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう話は会ってすぐに言うか、
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:42.36,Default,Light,0,0,0,,You should've told me this either as soon as we met, {\alpha&HFF&}or written it as part of the explanations in the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:45.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノートの使い方の説明にでも、書いておくべきじゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've told me this either as soon as we met, or written it as part of the explanations in the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:48.03,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Err.. I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:47.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう、そうだな…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.85,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,He doesn't fear me in the slightest, even though I'm a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:53.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮にも死神であるオレを恐れる事も無く、媚びる事もなく、
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:56.90,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,He doesn't try to suck up to me, and he keeps on relentlessly asking such probing questions of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:56.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こういう事に関してはがんがん突っ込んでくる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:02.76,Default,Light,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:02.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で、
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:03.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:08.25,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Is there anything else you should have told me beforehand, Ryuk the Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:06.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう前もって言っておくべき事はないんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死神リューク
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.62,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,No, there's nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:10.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ、もうない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:12.08,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:11.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(…多分)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:14.60,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Oh. That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:14.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか、残念だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.75,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,A shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:15.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残念？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.90,Default,Light,0,0,0,,If it was wings instead of eyes, {\alpha&HFF&}I might have seriously considered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目でなく翼だったら、
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本気で取引を考えたかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was wings instead of eyes, I might have seriously considered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:24.27,Default,Light,0,0,0,,It seems quite fitting for a god to have wings and fly freely across the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:24.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,翼を持って空を自由に飛ぶなんて…神らしいじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:28.27,Default,Light,0,0,0,,After all, it's been man's dream since antiquity to be able to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:28.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人類が古代からずっと抱いてきた夢でもあるしね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.74,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,If you grew wings and flew around you'd stand out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:32.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,翼がはいて空を飛んだら目立つだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけで警察に捕まりそうだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:35.63,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,The police would probably be able to catch you purely on that basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今のは冗談だリューク
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:37.11,Default,Light,0,0,0,,I was joking, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:42.81,Default,Light,0,0,0,,With all the trading of eyes, wings or whatever, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd probably end up becoming a real Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:42.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし、そうやって目だの翼だの取引していくうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With all the trading of eyes, wings or whatever, I'd probably end up becoming a real Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:45.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつの間にか本当の死神にされてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.49,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Although, I guess that could be quite an interesting concept too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:48.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう話も面白いじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.54,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:52.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心しろ、そんな事しなくてもライト、
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.58,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Even without doing anything like that, {\alpha&HFF&}you're already a worthy Shinigami, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without doing anything like that, you're already {\alpha&HFF&}a worthy Shinigami, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:56.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前はもう…立派な死神だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without doing anything like that, you're already a worthy Shinigami, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:00.84,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Right now, the World of Shinigami is rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:00.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の死神界は腐ってるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They live a vague and pointless existence, only taking human lives because they, themselves, are afraid to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:03.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ死にたくないという理由だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:08.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の寿命をいただき、漠然と生きている奴らばっかりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:13.81,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,They no longer understand why they even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:13.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何のために存在してるのかすら、もう誰にもわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:17.25,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,There's probably no meaning in their existence at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:16.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多分…存在してる意味なんて無いんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:21.20,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Compared to them, Light, {\alpha&HFF&}you're more of a Shinigami than they'll ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:20.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな死神よりライト、
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to them, Light, you're more of a Shinigami than they'll ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の方がよっぽと死神らしい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:30.29,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Well, by the sound of things, I'm doing a lot more work than them, {\alpha&HFF&}but I wouldn't want to be compared to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:29.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁ話は聞いてると、僕の方がよっぽと働いているみたいだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, by the sound of things, I'm doing a lot more work than them, but I wouldn't want to be compared to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死神と一緒にされたくないね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:37.32,Default,Light,0,0,0,,As a human, I'm using the Death Note to help humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:37.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は人間として、人間のためにデスノートを使っているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:44.75,Default,Light,0,0,0,,But it isn't like the World of Shinigami is of little importance to the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まぁしかし、人間にとっては、
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死神界は決して無意味な存在じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:47.35,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.86,Default,Light,0,0,0,,It's the truth. {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuk, even if Shinigami like you come down just once every hundred — no, thousand — years, the human world will change dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:48.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だってそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth. Ryuk, even if Shinigami like you come down just once every hundred — no, thousand — years, the human world will change dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:51.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リュークのような死神が百年…いや、
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,千年に一度でも降りてきただけで、
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間界は大きく変わるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:00.63,Default,Light,0,0,0,,The existence of the World of Shinigami is extremely significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:00.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐ろしく意味ある存在だよ、死神界は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.19,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,R-really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:01.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ、そうか…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:06.09,Default,Light,0,0,0,,If the World of Shinigami is really as rotten as you say it is, Ryuk, {\alpha&HFF&}why don't you try changing things when you get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の死神界がそこまで腐ってると言うのなら、
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リュークが帰った時、
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If the World of Shinigami is really as rotten as you say it is, Ryuk, why don't you try changing things when you get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:10.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間界に来た事を生かして、変えてみたらどうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.50,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Light, {\alpha&HFF&}you're turning out to be quite the positive thinker..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:17.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ライト、お前って本当は物凄くプラス思考な人間なのかもしれないな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, you're turning out to be quite the positive thinker..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.97,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり前じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:26.84,Default,Light,0,0,0,,You've got to be a positive thinker to think of using the Death Note to personally right the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:23.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前向きじゃなきゃ、デスノートを使って、
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:26.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自ら世界を良くしようなんて、思わないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.26,Default,Light,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:31.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.50,Default,Light,0,0,0,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:33.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.10,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,What's up? What do you "get"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:36.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした、何がわかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.90,Default,Light,0,0,0,,I've figured out how to obtain the name of my stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:42.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日僕を尾行してた奴の…名前を知る方法だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.65,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,What're you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:44.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする気だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,デスノートの使い方を利用するんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.97,Default,Light,0,0,0,,I'll be using the rules of the Death Note to my advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:53.91,Default,Light,0,0,0,,"Should a cause of death be specified, a further 6 minutes and 40 seconds are granted to write any further details".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:50.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「死因を書くと、さらに6分40秒、
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:53.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,詳しい死の状況を記載する時間が与えられる」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:58.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず、この『死の詳しい状況』がどの範囲まで自由にできるのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:55.23,Default,Light,0,0,0,,First, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll need to test just how free I am to specify the details of the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll need to test just how free I am to specify the details of the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:00.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,試させてもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:04.24,ps-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.34,MINOR SIGN,MINOR SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(356,394)\fad(700,0)}The next day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.26,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:08.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ、私だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:12.54,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,Another six prisoners?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また刑務所内の犯罪者が6人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.84,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,Due to heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:15.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心臓麻痺か？キラだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:15.96,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,It's got to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:17.52,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:21.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？三人が死の直前に今までいない行動？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:21.44,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,Three of them exhibited a pattern of behavior before death that we've never seen before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.39,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:22.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう事だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:25.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただの心臓麻痺じゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:25.32,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,You mean it wasn't just a normal heart attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ、死因は心臓麻痺なんですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.11,Default,Detective,0,0,0,,No. The cause of death was definitely a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.64,Default,Detective,0,0,0,,But directly before it happened, {\alpha&HFF&}one of them cut his own finger and drew a strange picture on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:32.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一人は死の直前、刑務所の壁に自分の指を切った血で、
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But directly before it happened, one of them cut his own finger and drew a strange picture on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奇妙な絵を描いています
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:37.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一人は、遺書とも何とも言えない文書を残しています
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:37.33,Default,Detective,0,0,0,,Another left an unexplainable note.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:42.84,Default,Detective,0,0,0,,The third managed to escape and seems to have made the effort to run all the way to the staff toilets before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:39.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fs14}　　　　　　たって{\fs24}\N三人目に達ては、
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:42.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脱走してわざわざ職員用のトイレの中で…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:50.45,Default,L,0,0,0,,What is it, Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:49.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたワタリ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:54.97,Default,Watari,0,0,0,,A few heart attack victims that acted slightly different from the usual have just been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:54.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先程、今までと少し違う心臓麻痺の被害者が出ました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.02,Default,L,0,0,0,,Different from the usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までと違う…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:00.66,Default,Watari,0,0,0,,I'm sending you the images of the text and picture they left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:07:00.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現場に残された絵と文書の画像を送ります
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.02,Default,L,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:01.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:06.67,Default,L,0,0,0,,This reads as though he's afraid of Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キラに怯えた文書…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:12.50,Default,L,0,0,0,,It could conceivably be merely the actions of a criminal, {\alpha&HFF&}but if Kira can control the time of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:11.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ単に犯罪者が取った行動とも取れるが…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It could conceivably be merely the actions of a criminal, but if Kira can control the time of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キラは死の時間を操れる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:18.97,Default,L,0,0,0,,What if Kira can also control the movements leading up to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:20.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしも死の直前の行動も操れる？としたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.16,Default,L,0,0,0,,In which case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.28,Default,L,0,0,0,,Chief, {\alpha&HFF&}regarding the most recent victims, I'd like to request that no details regarding their deaths are released other than that they died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:22.38,Ｌ-ja,,0,0,0,,局長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, regarding the most recent victims, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd like to request that no details regarding their deaths are released other than that they died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.01,Ｌ-ja,,0,0,0,,今回の犠牲者の件ですが、
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, regarding the most recent victims, I'd like to request that no details regarding their deaths are released other than that they died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:30.82,Ｌ-ja,,0,0,0,,報道関係には心臓麻痺以上の事は発表しないで下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:35.83,Ｌ-ja,,0,0,0,,キラが犯罪者によって何かのテストをしている可能性があります、
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:35.99,Default,L,0,0,0,,It's possible that Kira may be using these criminals to conduct some kind of test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:37.91,Default,L,0,0,0,,And if that is the case, {\alpha&HFF&}we shouldn't give them any easy answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:41.23,Ｌ-ja,,0,0,0,,だとすると…わざわざ答えを教えてやる事になりますので
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that is the case, we shouldn't give them any easy answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:42.54,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,I see..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:44.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど、わ、わかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:44.65,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.80,Default,Detective,0,0,0,,Performing tests on criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,犯罪者を使ってテスト!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,酷いな…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.56,Default,Detective,0,0,0,,Cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:51.97,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,It seems as though they enjoy playing games with people's lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:53.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の命をまるでゲームを楽しむかのように…絶対に許せん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.61,Default,ChiefYagami,0,0,0,,I won't forgive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:08:00.48,Default,L,0,0,0,,If Kira's really experimenting on criminals... {\alpha&HFF&}what's their objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キラが犯罪者で実験をしているとしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が狙いだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kira's really experimenting on criminals... what's their objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:10.51,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Take a look at this, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見ろよリューク
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:16.35,Default,Light,0,0,0,,The results of yesterday's six tests have already been entered into dad's computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,父さんのパソコンには、
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう昨日の六人のテスト結果が打ち込まれている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:20.64,Default,Light,0,0,0,,The Death Note is even more useful than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思った通りの結果だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使えるよ、デスノートは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.64,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,What d'ya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう意味だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:26.69,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Having escaped, one of them ran to a toilet that I'd specified in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:26.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一人は脱走してから、ノートに指定したトイレに行き
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:30.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一人は、僕がノートに書いた絵と同じ絵を壁に書き
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:31.44,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Another drew the exact picture that I'd drawn in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:35.86,Default,Light,0,0,0,,And another wrote the same sentences that I wrote in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:35.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一人は、僕がノートに書いた文書と同じ文書を残した
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:40.45,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Those three did exactly what I intended them to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:40.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この三人は、僕の思い通りになったわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:45.29,Default,Light,0,0,0,,For the remaining three, I purposely wrote circumstances that would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:45.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他の三人は、わざとかなり無理な死の状況を書いてみたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:45.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:51.10,Default,Light,0,0,0,,First, I wrote that the victim would die in an hour's time in front of the Eiffel Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:50.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず、「一時間後にフランスのエッフェル塔の前で死ぬ」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:56.68,Default,Light,0,0,0,,It's physically impossible for a prisoner in Japan to reach France in just an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:54.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日本の刑務所にいた人間が、一時間後にフランスなんて、
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,物理的に不可能だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:09:00.18,Default,Light,0,0,0,,As a result, this doesn't actually happen, and the victim simply dies of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:09:00.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこれは実現せず、ただの心臓麻痺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:05.98,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Next, I wrote "Draws an exact picture of L's face on the wall" in the Death Note,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:06.01,Default-ja,,0,0,5,,次は、「刑務所の壁に\N{\fs14} {\fnCloister Black\fe120\fs30}L{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs8} {\fs24}そっくりの似顔絵を書く」とデスノートに書いたが、
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's impossible to draw somebody you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:08.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知らない人間の顔は描けない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.57,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:19.12,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Lastly, I specified that the final victim should write, "I know that L is suspicious of the police force".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして最後の一人には
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:18.84,Default-ja,,0,0,5,,「俺は{\fs14} {\fnCloister Black\fe120\fs30}L{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs14} {\fs24}が日本警察を疑っている事を知っている」\Nそう書け残すように指示した
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:23.44,Default,Light,0,0,0,,I thought that this one might work, but it didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:23.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これはもしかしたらいけるかと思ったが…実行されなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:27.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり、本人の知らない情報や、考えもしない、
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:31.50,Default,Light,0,0,0,,If someone doesn't know a piece of information, they can't think of it, and so it'd be unnatural for that person to write it down, meaning they won't be able to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:31.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その人間が書くには不自然過ぎる事は書けないって事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:36.06,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Even the Death Note cannot accomplish the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:35.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,要するに、いくらデスノートでも、あり得ない事はできない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:43.60,Default,Light,0,0,0,,But, if it's within the realistic limits of what they can do, I can control them as much as I like before they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:40.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし、その人間がやってもおかしくない範囲の行動なら…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:43.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくらでも動かしてから死なせる事ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:48.85,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,I've got that much, but what are ya trying to achieve, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがわかったが…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:48.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で、何が狙いなんだ、ライト？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:53.61,Default,Light,0,0,0,,L and the police will never be able to guess my true objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:52.92,Default-ja,,0,0,5,,{\fs14} {\fnCloister Black\fe120\fs30}L{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs14} {\fs24}も警察も、僕の真意には絶対に気付けない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:59.70,Default,Light,0,0,0,,The famous detective will be too busy investigating the mystery of those pictures and messages...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:57.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名探偵は当分…犯罪者の残した絵や文書を謎解きに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夢中でいるに違いない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:03.70,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Those completely meaningless "dying messages".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:03.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全く意味がない…ダイングメッセージのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:11.92,Default,L,0,0,0,,If Kira is really using criminals as test subjects, it must be because they're about to begin something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:09.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キラが犯罪者を使って何らかのテストをしたとするなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:11.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かを始めるのために…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.13,Default,L,0,0,0,,If they make a move now, {\alpha&HFF&}there's the possibility that their suspicious actions will be picked up by the FBI...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:18.25,Default-ja,,0,0,1,,今動き出せば、\N不審な行動を取る人物が{\fs2} {\fnMonotype Corsiva\fe120\fs32}FBI{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs24}{\fs18} {\fs24}の目に留まる可能性も…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If they make a move now, there's the possibility that their suspicious actions will be picked up by the FBI...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.12,Default,L,0,0,0,,But... {\alpha&HFF&}If there's another reason they're doing this, other than to run tests...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:22.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ…もしテスト以外の目的があったとしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But... If there's another reason they're doing this, other than to run tests...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:26.86,Default,L,0,0,0,,There might be a message in the drawings and text.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:26.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この文書や絵を…何かのメッセージ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:28.94,Default,L,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:28.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これか…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:32.34,ps-ja,,0,0,5,,（{\fs14} {\fnCloister Black\fe120\fs22}L{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs8} {\fs18}、知っているか）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:32.44,Note,NOTE,0,0,0,,The upper line reads "L, did you know?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.27,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Alright, it's finally time for the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:33.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあいよいよ本番だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.28,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Real deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:35.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本番？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.28,Default,Light,0,0,0,,I'll use this drug addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日ニュースでやっていた、
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:43.83,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Yesterday, he attempted to rob a bank, but failed to take any money, and escaped by shooting employees and members of the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:42.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,銀行を襲ったが金を奪えず、一般人を襲って逃げた麻薬常習犯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:44.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつを使う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.08,Default,Light,0,0,0,,It's slightly last minute, but I'm sure it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:46.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当日だけどなんとかなるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:49.25,Default,Light,0,0,0,,I'll try asking a few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:48.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何人が当ってみよう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.60,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,"Try asking a few people"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何人か…当る？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.78,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Yeah. {\alpha&HFF&}Despite my appearance, I'm actually quite popular with the ladies, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:56.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ、こう見えても僕はけっこうモテるんだよ、リューク
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Despite my appearance, I'm actually quite popular with the ladies, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.39,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,..Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:06.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしもし？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:10.98,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Light?! Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:10.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え、月？お…おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:16.00,HOW TO USE IT-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:20.84,HOW TO USE IT-ja,,0,0,1,,{\fad(700,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:34.25,Default,Light,0,0,0,,He's still following me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:33.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,尾行はついているな…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:35.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:40.13,Default,Light,0,0,0,,If he wasn't, what I'm about to do would be pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:39.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,尾行がいないと、これからやる事の意味が無くなってしまう…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.43,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.76,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,A date, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,デートか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:49.43,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:49.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:52.27,Default,Light,0,0,0,,However you look at it, it's just a normal date.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どう見ても思いっ切りデートさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:55.52,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Even the guy that's following me can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕を尾行している奴から見てもね…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただのデートじゃないだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.27,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,But it isn't just a "normal" date, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:01.07,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,You mentioned something about knowing how to figure out your stalker's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:12:01.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,尾行者の名前を知る方法がわかったと言ってたが…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.99,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,What the hell do you plan on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体何をするつもりなんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.78,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Huh, Ryuk? {\alpha&HFF&}Didn't you see what I wrote in the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:05.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれリューク
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, Ryuk? Didn't you see what I wrote in the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:08.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕がデスノートに何を書いたか、見ていなかったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:12.62,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,No. Otherwise it'd be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:12.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ、それ見じゃと詰まらないからな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.75,Default,Light,0,0,0,,In that case, just be patient and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったらどうなるかおとなしく見てろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.61,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Sorry. Have you been waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめん、待たせちゃったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.52,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,No. Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:20.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううん、全然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:24.59,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,More importantly, I haven't been to Space Land since Junior High!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:25.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それよりスペースランドなんて、中学の時以来、楽しみ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.20,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも今日はライトと二人きりだし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:28.79,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,And we get to spend the entire day together, just the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:29.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…うん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:35.65,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,If he goes out on a weekday, he either goes to school or cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:35.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,平日は…外出といったら、学校と予備校に行くくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.14,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,On the odd day off, he goes on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たまの休みにデートか…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:42.86,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,Seems pretty normal. An earnest final year exam student.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:39.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いたって普通…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや、真面目な受験生だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:46.19,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,Police Chief Yagami's son, Light - {\alpha&HFF&}no need for suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:47.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜神局長の息子、月、疑う余地無し
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Police Chief Yagami's son, Light - no need for suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:54.86,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,I'll just check his movements today, and then that'll be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:54.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とりあえず、今日一日の行動を観て、終りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:04.65,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,But Light, didn't you say that we weren't going to go out until the exams are over?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:04.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも月、受験終わるまでは遊ばないとか言ってなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:08.09,Default,Light,0,0,0,,I guess it's okay, since I placed first in the national mock exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:07.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああそれは、全国模試一位の立場だがな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.47,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Eww, no need to be so smug.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぇ、感じ悪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:44.78,Default,Light,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来た！奴だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:45.80,Default,Light,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:51.39,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Seven passengers, excluding him... {\alpha&HFF&}in that case, everything should proceed smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:50.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,乗客は奴を除いて7人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven passengers, excluding him... in that case, everything should proceed smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:53.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これなら全て…うまく行く！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:56.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.98,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,I'm taking over this bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このバスはオレが乗っ取った！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:03.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バ、バスジャック!?こんな時に…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.40,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,A bus hi-jack?! At a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:07.74,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Keep it down! I'll kill anyone who dares to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:04.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騒ぐんじゃねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しでも動いた奴はぶっ殺すぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:13.32,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Oi, driver! D'ya know the phone number of the Space Land offices?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:13.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運転手、スペースランドの事務所の電話番号は…\N知ってるな！掛けろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:14.75,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Call 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:14.75,Default,Driver,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:14.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:18.71,Default,Driver,0,0,0,,This is driver Sasaki, of bus number 124.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1745車のドライバー佐々木です
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.91,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Tell 'em what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:20.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の状況を教えてやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:25.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ち…銃を持った男に、バスを…ジャックされました！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.07,Default,Driver,0,0,0,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}I've been hi-hacked by a man with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I've been hi-hacked by a man with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:26.22,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Give it 'ere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貸せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.88,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,You heard what's going on? Now, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ということだ、よく聞け！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:37.73,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,I want a woman in a car to bring yesterday's takings to the bus stop two stops away from Space Land before this bus gets there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日の売り上げをスペースランド二つ手前のバス停まで、
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,女が一人で車で持ってこい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:37.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バスが着く前にだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:44.50,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,If you call the police, or try anything funny, I'll kill every single person on this bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:41.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下手な小細工したり、警察に知らせたりしたら、
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:44.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,乗客を一人ずつぶっ殺す！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:55.70,LongNote,NOTE,0,0,0,,{\fs20.338983}Yuri-chan, don't worry; it's okay. \NI'll find an opportunity to disarm him. \NMy father's a police officer and I've \Nlearnt how to counter-attack such a scenario. \NHe looks small and relatively weak. \NI'm stronger than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:57.68,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Yuri-chan, don't worry; it's okay. I'll find an opportunity to disarm him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ユリちゃん、安心して
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:57.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,犯人の隙を見て僕が、ピストルを持った手を押さえる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,危険だ、やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:14:59.71,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,You can't, it's too dangerous. Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その時は、私がやる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:01.88,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,If it comes to that, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:06.63,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,It's okay, you don't need to communicate in writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:06.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ、筆談などしなくても、
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:10.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小声なら、走行音でここの会話は、犯人には聞こえない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:10.05,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,The noise of the bus is enough to cover up hushed conversations from the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:15.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの犯人と共犯者でないという…証拠ありますか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:15.85,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof that you're not an accomplice to this crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:17.26,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,A-{\alpha&HFF&}an accomplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:17.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きょ…共犯!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A-an accomplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:19.81,Default,Light,0,0,0,,It's a fairly common practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:19.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よくあるケースだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:27.02,Default,Light,0,0,0,,The culprit fools us into thinking he's alone, but secretly plants an accomplice at the back, just in case anything goes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,犯人は一人と思わせておいて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:26.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いざという時の為に、\Nあらかじめ後方からの見張りを置いておく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.86,Default,Light,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:29.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしました？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.03,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,No, no way, it can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:31.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やだ、まさか本当に…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:32.83,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}I don't have a choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:33.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,し、仕方がない…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't have a choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.54,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,There's no way Yagami Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜神ライトは、キラであるわけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:39.64,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,If he was, then he'd be able to kill the culprit with a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:39.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キラなら、犯人を心臓麻痺で殺せるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.96,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,Here's my proof. Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが証拠だ、見てくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.35,Default-ja,,0,0,-1,,{\fs2} {\fnMonotype Corsiva\fe120\fs32}FBI!?{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs24}{\fs18} {\fs24}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:45.86,Default,Light,0,0,0,,FBI!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:51.88,Default,Light,0,0,0,,So that's who L's been using to investigate the Japanese police!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:51.11,Default-ja,,0,0,-1,,そうか…{\fs14} {\fnCloister Black\fe120\fs30}L{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs8} {\fs24}は{\fs2} {\fnMonotype Corsiva\fe120\fs32}FBI{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs24}{\fs18} {\fs24}を使って、日本警察関係者を調べさせていたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.27,Default,Light,0,0,0,,His name is {\alpha&HFF&}Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名前は…レイ{\fs28\fn華康古印體}．{\fs24\fnMS PGothic}ペンバー
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:58.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信用します
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.53,Default,Light,0,0,0,,I'll trust you, {\alpha&HFF&}and for the time being I won't question what an FBI agent is doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll trust you, and for the time being I won't question what an FBI agent is doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:04.25,Default-ja,,0,0,-1,,今はあえて、\Nなぜ{\fs2} {\fnMonotype Corsiva\fe120\fs32}FBI{\fnMS PGothic\fe128\fs24}{\fs18} {\fs24}の捜査官が、ここに乗り合わせたのかは聞きません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:05.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,銃は…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.35,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Do you have a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:06.77,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:06.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持っている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:10.30,Default,Light,0,0,0,,So if it comes to that, I'll be relying on you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:09.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では、いざという時は、お任せしていいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.03,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:10.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:14.95,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up! Do ya wanna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:14.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,静かにしろ！ぶっ殺されたいのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:16.91,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,That man! {\alpha&HFF&}He was on the Japanese news two days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:19.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男…二日前に、日本でニュースになっていた男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That man! He was on the Japanese news two days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:23.13,ps-ja,,0,0,0,,静かにしろって言ってんだろ、言うこと聞け
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:24.92,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,He robbed a bank, killed three people, and then fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:24.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,銀行を襲い、一般人三人を殺して逃げた麻薬常習犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:27.04,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,He's extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:26.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,極めて危険だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.45,Default,Light,0,0,0,,It's fine. {\alpha&HFF&}He'll never shoot us with that gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:31.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫、奴の銃は、絶対に僕達を撃たない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. He'll never shoot us with that gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:33.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいお前！お前動くな！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.89,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, you! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.64,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,What's on that bit of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:40.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だその紙は？てめぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:41.30,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Why you--! {\alpha&HFF&}You passing notes around to try plotting against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:43.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,乗客同士メモで相談してやがたのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you--! You passing notes around to try plotting against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.10,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,Shit! {\alpha&HFF&}If he finds that note from before... he'll realize that we're waiting for an opportunity to overpower him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずい！さっきのメモを見られたら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! If he finds that note from before... he'll realize that we're waiting for an opportunity to overpower him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼が隙を見て、奴に飛びかかろうとしていた事が…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:53.99,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Huh? Just arrangements for a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:53.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けっ、デートの約束かよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.89,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,What a load of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くだらねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:58.62,Default,Light,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:58.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.33,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:10.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だてめぇは！…そこの一番後ろの奴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.25,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,You! The guy right at the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な…何ふざけてやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:13.47,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,い…いつからそこにいた！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:16.05,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Since when have you been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:19.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ？オレのことか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:20.03,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Huh? You talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:22.27,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,You can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おまえ、オレの姿が見えるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:24.68,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Don't move! {\alpha&HFF&}I-I'll shoot you, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:23.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,う…動くがねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move! I-{\alpha&HFF&}I'll shoot you, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,う…撃つぞバケモノー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move! I-I'll shoot you, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.15,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,This isn't good.. he's hallucinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:28.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずい！幻覚を見ている
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.29,Default,RayePenber,0,0,0,,Everyone, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:29.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな伏せろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.53,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:34.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ、そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:41.37,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,That note with the arrangements for the date was written on paper from the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきライトの落としたデートの約束メモ、
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,デスノートを切って書いたものだったわけが…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:46.67,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,And he made this guy touch it, so this guy's the only one who's able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:46.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして、こいつにメモを触らせて、こいつにだけオレの姿を見せる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.46,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あったまいい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.00,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:49.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,く…来るな！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.15,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:57.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いな、オレは死神だからそんなものじゃ死なないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:57.26,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,You know, I'm a Shinigami, so things like that won't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:13.44,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,"Those who touch the Death Note are able to see me."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:12.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「デスノートに触った者にはオレの姿が見える」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.91,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,"I will always have to follow Light around."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:16.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オレは「ライトの後をついていなければならない」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.90,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,"Shinigami won't die just by being shot."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:19.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「死神は銃で撃たれても死なない」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:22.66,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,These are all things I've told Light in the past, {\alpha&HFF&}and this is just the kind of practical application I'd expect from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:21.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなオレがライトに言った事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all things I've told Light in the past, and this is just the kind of practical application I'd expect from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:27.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすが全国表通模試一位、応用力がある
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:32.84,Default,Ryuk,0,0,0,,And he's managed to use this hi-jacking to get the name of the guy that's been following him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:32.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして、このバスジャックを利用して、\N尾行してた奴の名前もなんなくゲットか…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:36.47,Default,Hijacker,0,0,0,,Stop the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,車を止めて…ドア開けろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:06.67,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Exactly 11:45.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:08.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャスト11時45分、全て予定通り…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:08.33,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Everything went according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.50,Default,Light,0,0,0,,Oosoreda Kiichirou... death by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:12.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐田奇一郎、事故死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:22.64,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,Boards the 11:31-bus to Space Land from the bus station at the east entrance to the park, with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:22.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,公園東口バス停より、午前11時31分発、\Nスペースランド行きのバスに、銃を持って乗り込み
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世の物とは思えぬ幻影を見て、
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:30.06,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,Appears to have some out-of-this-world type of hallucination and empties his gun towards it. Disembarks from the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:29.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに向かって全弾を発砲し、バスから逃走…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:36.28,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,Immediately afterwards; same day; 11:45 - dies in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:36.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その直後、同日11時45分…事故に遭え死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:44.14,Default,Light,0,0,0,,The Death Note never fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:43.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,デスノートに狂いなし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:50.90,Default,Light,0,0,0,,It's your turn next... {\alpha&HFF&}Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:52.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次はあなたの番だ…レイ{\fs28\fn華康古印體}．{\fs24\fnMS PGothic}ペンバー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn next... Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.84,SIGN,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(565,302)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:14.78,Default-ja,,0,0,40,,思った通りだ…彼はまったく僕を疑ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:18.95,Default-ja,,0,0,40,,残りの捜査官たちも全員心臓麻痺…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:22.22,Default-ja,,0,0,40,,さよなら…レイ{\fs28\fn華康古印體}．{\fs24\fnMS PGothic}ペンバー
